response.original_title: 4K Revolution Costume Is Cute But...I Can't Stop Ichika Matsumoto Vol.2
response.overview: CSPL-019: 4K revolution! The second CosDeluxe edition of Ichika Matsumoto, the lovely and cute hyper great slender shaved AV actress representing Reiwa...that popular character that has existed since the early days of cosplay! Moreover, the tiger print bikini fits Ichika Matsumoto's slender body perfectly...a must-see for Ichika fans. In this work, Ichika Matsumoto's innocent and spoiled side is on full display. Ichika is so cute that she is jealous of Yakimochi who suspects him of cheating and gives her a cute punishment! “Darling is the only one Ichika likes.” Creampie & ejaculation on the tongue... 2 shots in total. Enjoy 65 minutes of cosplay with Ichika!
